data.description: Welcome to 2501 Haddenham Lane, this 4-bed, 2.5-bath gem in Cobb County's Bentley Park. Recently updated, including hardwood floors and a modern kitchen, this home seamlessly blends luxury with convenience. Enjoy a vaulted-ceiling den, a deck overlooking a private wooded backyard, and a finished basement with a media/playroom, an extra bedroom, and ample storage. Located just minutes from Smyrna Village, Downtown Marietta, and Truist Park-The Battery, this residence offers 3,756 sqft of living space and was built in 1999. Don't miss the chance to experience the perfect combination of charm and functionalityaschedule your private showing today!
